s restricting the use of", "bbox": [93.8, 1366.2, 1144.4, 1385.0]}, {"text": "decommissioning trust funds to rely on those conditions in lieu of compliance with NRC regulations.  FPL Energy's nuclear plants", "bbox": [93.8, 1387.9, 1144.5, 1406.6]}, {"text": "contain such restrictions in their NRC operating licenses.  With respect to the decommissioning trust fund for FPL Energy's", "bbox": [93.8, 1409.5, 1144.5, 1428.2]}, {"text": "Seabrook nuclear plant, decommissioning trust fund contributions and withdrawals are also regulated by the NDFC pursuant to", "bbox": [93.8, 1431.1, 1144.4, 1449.9]}, {"text": "New Hampshire law.", "bbox": [93.8, 1452.7, 260.3, 1471.5]}]}